  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "コロンブスの冒険をテーマにした歴史シミュレーションゲーム。黄金の夜明けを求めて。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "romu"
    },
    {
      "text": "A nautical strategic RPG hybrid action in the vein of Uncharted Waters. You follow the life of Christopher Columbus as he goes from rookie captain to his landing in America. After a few tutorial missions, you get turned loose on an open world to build fame for yourself by doing quests, slaying rare monsters holed up in dungeon areas, etc., until a King of a prominent country can be convinced to support your expedition to the New World.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    }
  ],
  "first_release_date": "1992-11-27",
